sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Registry as front_registry
    participant Policy as Capabilities / Policy / Prereqs
    participant Sensor as repo_health.run_frontier
    participant Plugins as Health Plugins
    participant Runtime as runtime_health
    participant Frontier as out/frontier/latest.csv
    participant Office as office.main
    participant Briefs as bundles + staff_briefs
    participant Human as Human Block

    Registry->>Sensor: project rows
    Policy->>Sensor: receptor rules
    Sensor->>Sensor: compute EffectiveRunSet
    Sensor->>Plugins: execute selected probes
    Plugins-->>Sensor: PASS / WARN / FAIL / INELIGIBLE
    Sensor->>Frontier: write latest local frontier
    Sensor->>Runtime: write current project health
    Sensor->>Plugins: append PluginResults

    Runtime->>Office: current health marker surface
    Registry->>Office: project inventory
    Office->>Office: compile expressed / latent / support / watch
    Office->>Briefs: package selected support/escalation fronts
    Briefs->>Human: focus packet / healthcheck / unlocker
    Human->>Human: MAINT or FOCUS
    Human-->>Office: POST evidence + next pointer